OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1781273476
OL,3,COver 340 jobs created at tech firm to
OL,4,Cmeet AI demand
OL,6,FMore than 340 new jobs are to be
OL,7,Fcreated at the technology company
OL,8,FKainos over the next three years to
OL,9,Fhelp meet customer demand for
OL,10,Fartificial intelligence (AI).
OL,12,FThe new roles are across software
OL,13,Fengineering, platform and data
OL,14,Fengineering, AI and data science,
OL,15,Farchitecture, product and Workday
OL,16,Fconsulting.
OL,18,FThere will also be roles in delivery,
OL,19,Fdesign and business support.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
