FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1781273476
OL,3,COver 340 jobs created at tech firm to
OL,4,Cmeet AI demand
OL,6,FThe jobs have an average salary of
OL,7,F#58,000.
OL,9,FMost will be located in Belfast with
OL,10,F32 positions based in Londonderry.
OL,12,FKainos said the investment will allow
OL,13,Fthem to "do more for customers as they
OL,14,Fput AI to work".
OL,16,FThe company, based at Crescent Gardens
OL,17,Fin Belfast, employs more than 3,500
OL,18,Fstaff across Europe and North America.
OL,20,FIt was established in 1986 and opened
OL,21,Fits second office in Derry in 2011.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
