PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1781273476
OL,3,COver 340 jobs created at tech firm to
OL,4,Cmeet AI demand
OL,6,FInvest NI has provided #1.5 million
OL,7,Ftowards the creation of the jobs.
OL,9,FChief Executive of Kainos, Brendan
OL,10,FMooney said: "This expansion reflects
OL,11,Fgrowing customer demand for our AI
OL,12,Fdigital transformation services across
OL,13,Fthe public, health and commercial
OL,14,Fsectors.
OL,16,F"By investing in our people, including
OL,17,F200 early career roles alongside these
OL,18,Fexperienced positions, we will be able
OL,19,Fto do more for our customers as they
OL,20,Fput AI to work."
OL,26,@rD@NOU
