OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1781273476
OL,3,COver 340 jobs created at tech firm to
OL,4,Cmeet AI demand
OL,6,FThe Economy Minister described the
OL,7,Fcreation of the jobs as a "strong vote
OL,8,Fof confidence in our growing tech
OL,9,Fsector and the highly skilled people
OL,10,Fwho work here".
OL,12,FCaoimhe Archibald said the expansion
OL,13,Fhighlights how "businesses can scale,
OL,14,Finnovate and create rewarding careers
OL,15,Ffor local talent, with AI driving new
OL,16,Fhigh-value job creation across the
OL,17,Feconomy".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
